2004-11-06  Ronald S. Bultje  <rbultje@ronald.bitfreak.net>

	* docs/pwg/advanced-scheduling.xml:
	* docs/pwg/advanced-tagging.xml:
	* docs/pwg/advanced-types.xml:
	* docs/pwg/building-boiler.xml:
	* docs/pwg/building-chainfn.xml:
